Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================OP============================
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.82,0:02:30.81,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}茫茫人海行色匆匆　擦肩而过碰撞纠缠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.01,0:02:36.93,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}感受彼此羽翼的伤痛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.26,0:02:43.12,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}用寂寞抱紧你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.71,0:02:49.57,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}无须其他任何表示
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.00,0:02:52.94,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}等候交融的瞬间　觉醒的永恒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.13,0:02:55.99,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}心急如焚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.46,0:03:02.52,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}时光荏苒转瞬即逝　
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.69,0:03:11.99,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}只能叹息　心愿遥不可及
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.25,0:03:18.29,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}炽热的灵魂　传递真情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.41,0:03:21.49,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}不再有保留
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.65,0:03:27.84,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}你曾经的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.59,0:03:33.12,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}又在何方…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================ED============================
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.22,0:22:11.85,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(500,1500)\an3}曾如此形影不离
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.17,0:22:20.94,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(500,2500)\an3}黄昏却已变色…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.72,0:22:37.28,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}平凡的温柔　让你远去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.53,0:22:45.01,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}被抛弃的心灵　四处彷徨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.33,0:22:53.24,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}这份失落　如果就是生活
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.44,0:22:57.52,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}我愿在夜空下　从此闭上双眼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.80,0:23:06.55,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}曾形影不离　黄昏却已变色
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.80,0:23:17.77,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,1000)}{\be1}至少让我在月光下　静静入眠…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================Avant============================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.71,0:00:03.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿救来的平民作人质
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.33,0:00:06.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那种卑鄙的家伙为伍
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.98,0:00:08.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是你的正义吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.54,0:00:09.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.99,0:00:11.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.42,0:00:14.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会救出她
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.58,0:00:15.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.76,0:00:17.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.91,0:00:20.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是说「会没事的」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.10,0:00:23.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说「我们也去 会没事的」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.99,0:00:27.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么没保住爸爸的船？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.76,0:00:32.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么没把他们都干掉？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.65,0:00:35.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙蕾 基拉尽力了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.45,0:00:38.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 因为自己也是调整人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.91,0:00:41.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以没尽全力战斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.76,0:00:45.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和他都是善良的人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.01,0:00:48.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这真是件悲哀的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.67,0:00:51.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也认识阿斯兰？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.27,0:00:53.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰·萨拉是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.99,0:00:56.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我未来的丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.14,0:00:59.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然人很不错
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.03,0:01:01.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却非常沉默寡言
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.96,0:01:05.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈罗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.45,0:01:07.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 这只哈罗就是他送我的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.96,0:01:09.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈罗哈罗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.41,0:01:11.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 真的是那样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.65,0:01:15.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 卡兹？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.63,0:01:19.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那架被抢走的机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.62,0:01:20.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神盾什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.71,0:01:23.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驾驶它的人 好像是基拉的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.74,0:01:29.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉 你会回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.50,0:01:36.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你们在干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.67,0:01:39.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.92,0:01:41.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到我们这里来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.27,0:01:43.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.74,0:01:46.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我保证
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.32,0:01:49.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉 你也一起来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.28,0:01:52.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有什么理由要留在地球军？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.51,0:01:58.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我其实 也不想和你战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.77,0:02:03.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 那艘船上有我要保护的人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.04,0:02:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有朋友在！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================Main============================
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.34,0:03:41.55,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1176,576)}{\fad(500,500)}{\bord3\shad1\be20\an3\fs60}觉醒之刃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.15,0:03:46.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被告方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.57,0:03:49.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就自己行为对舰船安全的危害性
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.21,0:03:51.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本毫无认识
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.57,0:03:55.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的发言只是个人臆测
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.42,0:03:58.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要求从议事录中删除
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.52,0:04:01.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,允许删除
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.49,0:04:02.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.39,0:04:06.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将平民抓作人质
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.53,0:04:09.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从根本上违反了科西嘉条约
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.75,0:04:11.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本次的行为
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.43,0:04:13.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可参照该条约特例项C
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.77,0:04:16.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战时特例
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.28,0:04:17.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.65,0:04:19.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特例项C？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.31,0:04:21.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼知道还有这条
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.26,0:04:27.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…但是正因为释放了人质
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.33,0:04:28.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纳斯卡级才撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.86,0:04:31.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也得以脱离险境
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.43,0:04:33.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不过是结果主义
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.15,0:04:38.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉·大和有什么想说的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.05,0:04:43.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么擅自行动？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.77,0:04:48.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为救她不是为了当作人质
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.58,0:04:50.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.38,0:04:52.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要当也是当女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.50,0:04:53.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我反对！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.57,0:04:57.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辩护人请注意措辞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.96,0:05:02.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉·大和的行为违反了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.84,0:05:05.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,军法第三条B项
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.58,0:05:07.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第十条F项
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.90,0:05:10.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第十三条3项
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.01,0:05:12.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本法庭判处当事人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.52,0:05:15.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枪毙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.00,0:05:20.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 这归根结底
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.96,0:05:22.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是军事法庭上的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.24,0:05:26.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本法庭没有裁决平民的权力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.11,0:05:28.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,望基拉·大和
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.94,0:05:31.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后切忌草率行事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.38,0:05:33.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本法庭就此闭庭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.54,0:05:36.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.17,0:05:39.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 今后要听话别擅自行事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.80,0:05:53.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.29,0:05:56.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.24,0:05:58.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.51,0:05:59.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.04,0:06:02.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要求你也打扫厕所一周？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.66,0:06:04.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.54,0:06:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这么办吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.71,0:06:14.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.39,0:06:15.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.60,0:06:18.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说…只有我们俩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.53,0:06:24.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛多克中士对我们大发雷霆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.33,0:06:28.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们知不知道“危险”两个字怎么写吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.86,0:06:30.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.15,0:06:31.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.39,0:06:34.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了 马上和第八舰队会合
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.45,0:06:35.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.24,0:06:40.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡兹说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.51,0:06:43.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到你和那个女孩的话了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.79,0:06:49.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驾驶神盾的 是你朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.33,0:06:57.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说实话 我挺担心的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.24,0:06:59.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赛…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.76,0:07:03.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过好在 你还是回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.07,0:07:08.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那回头见 我去换班
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.66,0:07:21.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要回来 基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.90,0:07:23.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.31,0:07:43.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实 可以在他们会合前追上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.83,0:07:46.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是那里距离月球舰队射程
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.44,0:07:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有十分钟不到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.41,0:07:50.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是有足足十分钟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.43,0:07:52.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胆小鬼就少说几句吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.77,0:07:56.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有十分钟 有足足十分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.16,0:07:58.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全在如何看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.52,0:08:00.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我看来有足足十分钟时间
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.96,0:08:03.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却眼睁睁看他们会合
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.13,0:08:04.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才是种耻辱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.80,0:08:07.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同意 奇袭的成败
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.67,0:08:09.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在乎行动时间长短
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.33,0:08:12.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这我当然明白…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.47,0:08:13.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅萨琉斯号
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.83,0:08:16.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将拉克丝移交给拉格尼队长的船后
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.82,0:08:18.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就会调头回来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.02,0:08:21.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此之前 由我们歼灭长腿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.38,0:08:23.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.60,0:08:24.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.04,0:08:27.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.21,0:08:39.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈罗哈罗 阿斯兰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.68,0:08:43.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉克丝…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.37,0:08:46.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈罗兴高采烈的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.80,0:08:49.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久没见你了 好像很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.77,0:08:53.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈罗没有这种感情程序
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.29,0:08:55.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你虽然是客人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.03,0:08:57.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但梅萨琉斯是艘军舰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.78,0:09:00.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要在屋外到处走动为好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.39,0:09:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到哪里都被要求这样 好无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.78,0:09:10.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法 身为军人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.18,0:09:19.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 阿斯兰？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.41,0:09:21.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.50,0:09:24.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想来看看你好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.86,0:09:28.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…他们说你被当成人质
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.28,0:09:32.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.17,0:09:33.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那边的船上时
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.67,0:09:36.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你朋友很照顾我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.96,0:09:39.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.79,0:09:43.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉先生为人很好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.94,0:09:46.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 也很坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.03,0:09:48.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.38,0:09:51.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘴上说自己不是军人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.54,0:09:52.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却还在驾驶那种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.52,0:09:55.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他只是在被利用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.89,0:09:57.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.89,0:10:01.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他父母是自然人 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.51,0:10:09.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说 并不想和你战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.05,0:10:11.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.47,0:10:14.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁会想和他…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.11,0:10:20.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉打扰 我先告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.47,0:10:24.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近每次见你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.38,0:10:27.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你总是这么愁眉不展
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.97,0:10:30.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑呵呵的打不了仗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.07,0:10:42.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有30分钟就到会合点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.64,0:10:44.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这航海总算快到头了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.93,0:10:46.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索敌 加强警戒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.01,0:10:48.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰队目标大
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.82,0:10:50.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心以他们为目标的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.15,0:10:52.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.39,0:10:56.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一路发生不少事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.06,0:10:58.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过就快到头了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.64,0:10:59.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.15,0:11:02.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们会放我们下船吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.56,0:11:03.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回地球
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.73,0:11:04.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.78,0:11:05.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还记得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.10,0:11:08.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时 拉米亚斯上尉她说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.54,0:11:10.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论出于何种原因
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.01,0:11:14.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目睹了军方重要机密的你们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.69,0:11:17.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我和相关方面取得联系
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.25,0:11:18.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并收到处理决定前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.07,0:11:21.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须留在我的监视范围内
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.28,0:11:25.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 所以舰队不就是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.81,0:11:28.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个“相关方面”吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.93,0:11:30.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.67,0:11:32.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.28,0:11:35.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉会怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.56,0:11:36.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们会放他走吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.68,0:11:39.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做了那么多事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.94,0:11:53.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙蕾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.37,0:12:15.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙蕾 没事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.52,0:12:16.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是再休息下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.06,0:12:18.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.04,0:12:25.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉 上次对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.35,0:12:31.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次我 头脑一片混乱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.77,0:12:33.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说了许多过分的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.63,0:12:36.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.11,0:12:38.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙蕾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.54,0:12:41.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那么拼命为了我们战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.77,0:12:43.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保护我们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.57,0:12:45.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我却…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.14,0:12:47.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙蕾 别这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.07,0:12:49.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.08,0:12:51.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.57,0:12:56.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也知道的 你很努力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.77,0:12:57.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.02,0:13:02.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 芙蕾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.65,0:13:03.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才应该道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.95,0:13:05.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没能保护好你父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.39,0:13:09.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战争真讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.53,0:13:12.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早点结束就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.35,0:13:15.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.54,0:13:21.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷达波遭到干扰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.91,0:13:23.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中子干扰反应增大
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.98,0:13:32.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全员一级战斗状态
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.36,0:13:38.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,103 橙色A 罗拉西亚级
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.96,0:13:40.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认机动战士热纹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.19,0:13:43.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是迅雷 暴风 决斗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.70,0:13:44.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.68,0:13:47.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼看就要会合了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.77,0:13:49.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全员一级战斗状态
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.34,0:13:53.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重复 全员一级战斗状态
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.46,0:13:56.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打仗了 又要打仗了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.90,0:14:03.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧 来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.47,0:14:06.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 大哥哥有急事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.44,0:14:12.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管又开战了 不过别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.07,0:14:16.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个大哥哥会保护我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.11,0:14:18.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.47,0:14:22.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 他会把坏人全部干掉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.75,0:14:24.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.69,0:14:34.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 要给我全杀光
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.81,0:14:37.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.82,0:14:45.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死 真会挑时候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.90,0:14:46.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有你们的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.22,0:14:49.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穆·拉·弗拉戈 出击
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.52,0:14:57.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉 扎夫特有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.11,0:14:59.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗拉西亚级1
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.45,0:15:01.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决斗 暴风 迅雷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.80,0:15:03.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是那三架
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.37,0:15:12.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,APU启动 装备空袭者背包
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.96,0:15:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连接弹射器
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.58,0:15:17.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强袭 待命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.39,0:15:20.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,系统正常
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.97,0:15:30.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,线路清空 强袭 出击
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.74,0:15:32.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉·大和 出击
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.33,0:15:45.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第八舰队正来接应 坚持住
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.44,0:15:48.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獾阵炮启动 反光束爆雷准备
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.83,0:15:50.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰尾导弹管全部待命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.27,0:16:05.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰船的回避模式被解析了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.63,0:16:14.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用机体隐藏射线
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.46,0:16:16.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺有噱头的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.86,0:16:27.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.32,0:16:33.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗拉戈上尉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.17,0:16:40.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引开机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.06,0:16:43.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼科尔 长腿交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.17,0:16:44.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.07,0:17:01.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小子叫强袭是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.81,0:17:09.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柏瑞安 发射
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.86,0:17:18.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丢失迅雷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.82,0:17:21.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它使用了海市蜃楼粒子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.46,0:17:24.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反光束爆雷 对空榴霰弹头
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.75,0:17:26.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反光束爆雷发射
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.91,0:17:29.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰尾导弹换装对空榴霰弹头
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.32,0:17:37.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据光束角度 计算迅雷所在位置
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.55,0:17:42.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,榴霰弹头 发射
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.09,0:17:55.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是自家造的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.55,0:17:57.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对弱点一清二楚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.31,0:18:01.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獾阵解除自动跟踪模式
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.58,0:18:02.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,张开弹幕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.25,0:18:18.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天你逃不了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.89,0:18:22.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能死在这里！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.30,0:18:38.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.45,0:18:51.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不规则回避运动
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.98,0:18:57.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈特弗里德瞄准 发射
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.19,0:19:07.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第六传感器阵列 中弹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.55,0:19:09.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,复合装甲内侧温度上升
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.53,0:19:18.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去装甲的散热跟不上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.66,0:19:20.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装甲内温度继续上升
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.31,0:19:23.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再中两发就支持不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.89,0:19:25.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,调头 右转舵20
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.44,0:19:27.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迅雷接近
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.25,0:19:31.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强袭和零式呢 在干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.50,0:19:33.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在与决斗和暴风交战中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.60,0:19:37.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好难缠
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.46,0:19:45.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,区区机动堡垒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.44,0:19:47.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碍手碍脚 快去死
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.34,0:19:56.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法用舰炮 强袭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.30,0:19:58.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉 基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.84,0:20:02.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被迅雷近身了 快回来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.42,0:20:08.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大天使号…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.55,0:20:14.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管又开战了 不过没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.60,0:20:18.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个大哥哥会保护我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.30,0:20:20.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.01,0:20:26.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能让大天使号…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.74,0:20:28.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被击沉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.16,0:20:36.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.56,0:20:45.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.48,0:20:50.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲开了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.32,0:20:57.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.51,0:21:07.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.17,0:21:21.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊扎克 伊扎克
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.06,0:21:23.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.85,0:21:25.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提亚哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.90,0:21:27.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼科尔 怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.31,0:21:28.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊扎克他
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.84,0:21:32.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼 好疼 好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.98,0:21:34.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊扎克
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.38,0:21:35.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提亚哥 撤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.85,0:21:36.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人舰队要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.99,0:21:37.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.23,0:21:47.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们撤了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.92,0:21:49.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得好 孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.58,0:21:51.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上尉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.84,0:21:54.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.31,0:21:59.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么 你小子真神了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.13,0:22:01.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.95,0:22:04.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是第八舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.01,0:22:11.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 全要给我杀光
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.69,0:22:21.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则 战争不会结束
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================Next============================
